StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [sp_DBAUpdateO.cerTLog]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
AS
INSERT INTO [HQQUA12026\REPORT].MCRISS_OLAP.DBO.OFFICER_TRANS_LOG SELECT T.TRANSACTION_ID, T.NWA_ID, T.ORGANIZATION_ID, T.TRAN_TYPE, T.TRAN_NAME, T.NEW_TRAN_VALUE, T.OLD_TRAN_VALUE, T.USER_LOGIN, T.TRANSACTION_DATE FROM MCRISS.dbo.OFFICER_TRANS_LOG T WHERE T.TRANSACTION_ID > ISNULL((SELECT MAX(T1.TRANSACTION_ID) FROM [HQQUA12026\REPORT].MCRISS_OLAP.DBO.OFFICER_TRANS_LOG T1),0)
